  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7, then take your <strong>chicken</strong> out of the fridge and open the packet to let it breathe before cooking</p><p>Add the <strong>ground almonds</strong>, <strong>half</strong> the <strong>ground paprika</strong> and <strong>half</strong> the <strong>cayenne pepper </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to a plate with a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>Nashville-style chicken coating</strong></p><p>Add 100ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]</span> <strong>milk alternative</strong> to a bowl</p>",
      "order": 1,
